ji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f42e8090bcbb8183d7d71bc9abd68bf63e7994","tid":1757690,"uid":171555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:06:36.000Z","msg":"周不時會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前排突然tg問我最近點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 分左手2年左右"}]}